## Implementation notes (for the meta-skill maintainer)
## ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# - All four commands share a common helper `_forks_request(method, path, **kw)`
#   that injects the API key header and surfaces 402 with a friendly upgrade
#   prompt linking to https://recipes.wisechef.ai/pricing#operator.
# - The fork tarball is built with `tar czf - --exclude=.git --exclude=node_modules .`
#   and streamed (chunked) so we don't double the 10 MB payload in memory.
# - Total addition: ~70 lines (well under the 200-line meta-skill cap).
